<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893528E0FF2AAFF29FCD1FF32" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147332" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="holotype">
The specimen here recognized as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793528E0FF030FF29FDBEFF1E" box="[525,623,187,213]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">holotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing labels “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693528E0FF1B7FF29FB92FF1E" authority="Ziegler" authorityName="Ziegler" box="[906,1091,187,213]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="suturalis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793528E0FF1B7FF29FC3DFF1E" box="[906,1004,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">suturalis</emphasis>
Ziegler
</taxonomicName>
h. in Dalmatia” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793528E0FF70CFF29FA4DFF1E" box="[1329,1436,187,213]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">Holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693528E0FF28BFF4DFDE5FF32" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[182,564,223,249]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="suturalis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793528E0FF28BFF4DFE44FF32" box="[182,405,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">Acupalpus suturalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF3A1FF4DFDE5FF32" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[412,564,223,249]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectorName id="2687537393528E0FF002FF4DFD7EFF32" box="[575,687,223,249]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">J. Serrano</collectorName>
vidit.”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93528E0FF2FAFE91FED9FE1A" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593528E0FF2FAFE91FB72FE42" blockId="11.[151,1437,187,465]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF2FAFE91FEB6FED6" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[199,359,259,285]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention the number of beetles he studied. From the brief description it is inferred that he only had a single specimen at hand. The beetle I hereby recognize as the 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793528E0FF1EBFEB5FBE9FE8A" box="[982,1080,295,321]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">holotype</typeStatus>
shows the dorsal dark colouration with the first elytron interval yellowish coloured, the punctures of pronotum basis and the smooth head without microsculpture, characters that are proper of the species (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF12AFEFDFC67FE42" author="Jeannel, R." box="[791,950,367,393]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel, 1942</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF1FCFEFDFB81FE42" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[961,1104,367,393]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" pagination="344 - 386" refId="ref12516" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2004) Harpalina. In: Freude, H., Harde, K. W., Lohse, G. A. &amp; Klausnitzer, B. (Eds.), Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Bd. 2 Adephaga 1: Carabidae (Laufkafer). Spektrum-Verlag, Heidelberg / Berlin, pp. 344 - 386." type="book chapter" year="2004">Wrase, 2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF666FEFDFB46FE42" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1115,1175,367,393]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593528E0FF2FAFE01FED9FE1A" blockId="11.[151,1437,187,465]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">
The species occurs in Central and Eastern Europe; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493528E0FF137FE01FC60FE66" author="Jeannel, R." box="[778,945,403,429]" pageId="11" pageNumber="495" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942)</bibRefCitation>
noted that it had been found only one time in 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593528E0FF289FE25FED5FE1A" box="[180,260,439,465]" name="France" pageId="11" pageNumber="495">France</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
